The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Wild card for Rohan
                                                                                                                       7                                      Wild card for Rohan
                      
	Chennai: On the basis of their talent and impressive results over the course of the year, Indian tennis players Rohan Bopanna and Yuki Bhambri have been awarded wild cards entries for the singles main draw of Aircel Chennai Open 2011 to be played here from January 3 to 9.         
	Somdev Devvarman, meanwhile, has also got a direct entry into the tournament on the merit of his ranking.         
	The tournament organisers have rewarded these two players due to their potential.... Along with Somdev Devvarman... and the reunion of Leander (Paes) and Mahesh (Bhupathi), the fans will have an opportunity to cheer for a strong Indian contingent, a release said. (PTI)                                                                                                                     
